- What?

02:55.920 --> 02:57.620
This is for you.

02:58.589 --> 03:00.390
Oh, my God! Is this real?

03:00.424 --> 03:01.358
- Totally real.
- It's a letter

03:01.392 --> 03:03.443
from Frida Kahlo to Diego.

03:03.494 --> 03:04.577
What?! Let me see that.

03:04.612 --> 03:05.662
No, you're not serious.

03:05.696 --> 03:06.730
Three hours of studio time.

03:06.764 --> 03:08.598
I hope it's enough.

03:08.632 --> 03:10.433
Dude, this guy recorded the Flaming Lips!

03:10.451 --> 03:11.534
This is amazing!

03:11.602 --> 03:13.236
- Thank you so much.
- You're welcome.

03:13.270 --> 03:14.537
- No, I can't accept...
- Please.

03:14.572 --> 03:17.223
With all the hospitality
in letting me stay here.

03:17.258 --> 03:19.275
Thank you so much. And this is...

03:19.309 --> 03:21.111
- for you.
- A cappuccino maker.

03:21.145 --> 03:23.263
I have been dying to get one of these!

03:23.297 --> 03:25.181
- You mentioned that once.
- Oh! Thank you!

03:25.216 --> 03:28.151
- I'm glad you like it.
- Um, did you get Daphne anything?

03:29.220 --> 03:30.320
- Oh, no.
- No no no no, it's okay.

03:30.354 --> 03:32.055
I don't... I don't need anything.

03:33.791 --> 03:35.759
Actually...

03:35.793 --> 03:38.895
