03:57.515 --> 04:00.250
- Uh, this is pretty rocking.
- Yee-haw!

04:03.354 --> 04:05.021
What do you think?

04:05.055 --> 04:06.356
It's...

04:06.390 --> 04:09.025
How is she supposed to drive this thing?

04:09.059 --> 04:10.960
- She will learn.
- Angelo, I know

04:10.995 --> 04:12.829
- that you meant well...
- Trust me.

04:12.863 --> 04:14.764
This is what she needs.

04:14.799 --> 04:16.766
Hello, sir. May I take your order?

04:16.801 --> 04:18.735
Uh, we gotta take this thing to Buckner.

04:18.769 --> 04:20.786
And I could help! I can help!

04:23.774 --> 04:25.608
