04:25.643 --> 04:26.743
Keep it for one week, okay?

04:26.777 --> 04:27.877
Just one week.

04:27.912 --> 04:29.412
Promise me.

04:30.815 --> 04:32.315
Sure.

04:32.349 --> 04:33.516
You're gonna love it!

04:34.751 --> 04:36.519
Look at you.

04:36.554 --> 04:38.538
All you need is a red
suit and a sleigh, huh?

04:38.572 --> 04:39.522
Yup! 

04:39.557 --> 04:41.191
Merry Christmas.

04:45.262 --> 04:46.229
Wow!

04:46.263 --> 04:48.148
Uh, yeah!

04:48.199 --> 04:51.034
What should we ask for next? A pony?

04:51.068 --> 04:53.036
Okay, so is he...

04:53.070 --> 04:54.220
richer than your parents?

04:54.271 --> 04:56.706
Or is it all sort of at the same level?

04:56.740 --> 04:58.875
Yeah, it's definitely not the same.

04:58.909 --> 05:01.844
And there are levels of richness.

05:01.862 --> 05:04.781
And rich people love to compare themselves

05:04.815 --> 05:07.484
