05:08.486 --> 05:11.421
He just looks so natural being rich.

05:11.455 --> 05:13.523
Doesn't he? Like it... it just fits him.

05:13.557 --> 05:15.558
Not like me or my mom.

05:15.593 --> 05:18.628
Do you think she's regretting
not taking the money?

05:18.662 --> 05:20.263
No way.

05:20.297 --> 05:22.265
Do you actually see my mom

05:22.299 --> 05:24.267
living off of Angelo's millions?

05:24.301 --> 05:26.102
She would cut off her right arm

05:26.136 --> 05:28.204
before she'd be some kept woman.

05:28.239 --> 05:30.874
First he punches out your boyfriend,

05:30.908 --> 05:33.076
then he just gives you a food truck.

05:33.110 --> 05:34.878
He definitely swings big.

05:34.912 --> 05:36.713
Well, I appreciate all the effort,

05:36.747 --> 05:38.848
but I am not driving around town

05:38.883 --> 05:41.551
selling corn dogs.

05:41.585 --> 05:42.685
You know, I don't think Merkie

05:42.720 --> 05:44.587
and Ivan Ronan have even spoken

05:44.622 --> 05:45.889
10 words to us over the years.

05:45.923 --> 05:47.524
Why would they invite us to golf?

05:47.558 --> 05:48.591
They must want something.

05:48.626 --> 05:49.692
When are we getting rid of that food truck?

05:49.727 --> 05:51.294
Next week?

05:51.328 --> 05:53.328
Oh! She's on the board of
that spinal cord charity.

05:53.330 --> 05:54.497
That must be it.

05:54.532 --> 05:56.366
I can't believe how you fawned
over that coffee machine.

05:56.400 --> 05:57.500
Yeah, well you say that,

05:57.535 --> 06:00.069
