06:00.104 --> 06:02.071
And then you encourage her
to actually use the truck?

06:02.106 --> 06:03.206
The dumbest gift in the world?

06:03.240 --> 06:05.808
I was just trying to be supportive.

06:05.843 --> 06:07.243
She's been so down lately.

06:07.278 --> 06:08.211
How about that car?

06:08.245 --> 06:10.013
Is that a cliché?

06:10.047 --> 06:12.615
Win a bunch of money, buy a sports car.

06:12.650 --> 06:13.917
Do you want me to put
the clubs in your Porsche?

06:13.951 --> 06:15.952
I earned my money.

06:15.986 --> 06:18.488
He's just never been able
to give her a present.

06:18.522 --> 06:20.423
He was just trying to...

06:20.457 --> 06:22.392
He's showing us up, Kathryn,
that's what he's doing.

06:22.426 --> 06:24.360
He rubbing our face in
the dollar... excuse me.

06:24.395 --> 06:26.663
The 66 cents that we actually won.

