tell people or anything?

17:51.587 --> 17:52.654
I don't know.

17:52.688 --> 17:54.489
I don't know anything
except that I'm screwed.

17:54.490 --> 17:56.358
Just give me some time.

17:56.392 --> 17:59.494
I need to try to deal with this.

17:59.528 --> 18:01.062
Okay?

18:00.997 --> 18:02.197
