18:05.835 --> 18:06.868
Son of a bitch.

18:06.902 --> 18:09.738
After all the money we pay them?

18:09.772 --> 18:11.039
And all the money I've raised for them?

18:11.073 --> 18:12.607
You know what? I always hated

18:12.642 --> 18:13.842
that Monsieur Feldman.

18:13.876 --> 18:15.677
It's actually pronounced... Feldman.

18:15.711 --> 18:18.546
Who's on this honor board anyway, huh?

18:18.581 --> 18:20.615
A bunch of brown nosers
passing judgment on their peers.

18:20.650 --> 18:23.401
How are they supposed to
decide if you cheated or not?

18:23.452 --> 18:24.552
Yeah.

18:24.587 --> 18:25.720
I have to present a case,

18:25.755 --> 18:27.522
Monsieur Feldman has to present a case.

18:27.556 --> 18:28.657
