18:49.745 --> 18:50.705
Give everybody presents?

18:50.713 --> 18:52.480
He's gonna speak in French

18:52.515 --> 18:54.582
and prove that he's real,

18:54.617 --> 18:56.551
and that's why I improved so much.

18:56.585 --> 18:59.254
Well, that's a great idea.

18:59.288 --> 19:01.539
I am so proud of you!

19:01.590 --> 19:04.175
- You're gonna do fine.
- Sweetie, I'm not so sure

19:04.226 --> 19:07.362
it's a great idea to have Angelo as
your backup in front of an honor board.

19:07.396 --> 19:09.397
Are you kidding me?

19:09.432 --> 19:11.366
Angelo and a jury? He'll
probably walk out of there

19:11.400 --> 19:13.234
with another million bucks.

19:13.269 --> 19:14.869
Good point.

