Hey, can you give me a hand?

19:21.744 --> 19:23.745
Oh, yeah. Sure.

19:25.881 --> 19:27.549
Thank you. Whoo.

19:27.583 --> 19:28.616
It's for Angelo's condo.

19:28.651 --> 19:29.968
I have to keep a bunch of things there

19:30.002 --> 19:31.586
