24:58.906 --> 24:59.906
but didn't follow directly...

24:59.940 --> 25:01.708
I see we've done some research.

25:01.742 --> 25:03.743
I think this is it, John.

25:03.778 --> 25:06.746
I think this is my next step.

25:07.848 --> 25:09.716
Run for office?

25:09.750 --> 25:11.584
I know this family has been through a lot,

25:11.619 --> 25:13.687
but I sort of think
that that's a good thing.

25:13.721 --> 25:16.673
I mean, we've been vetted
backwards and forwards by lawyers,

25:16.724 --> 25:19.559
we're used to being in the public eye

25:19.593 --> 25:22.529
and we don't have to bet the
whole farm on my campaign.

25:22.563 --> 25:23.530
Hold on, hold on.

25:23.564 --> 25:25.298
If you do this, we do this.

25:25.333 --> 25:27.367
We will support you in every way,

25:27.401 --> 25:30.103
whatever that means.

25:30.137 --> 25:32.138
So you see it? You kinda see it now?

25:32.173 --> 25:34.274
Well, I'm starting to.

25:36.110 --> 25:37.277
Okay, so,

25:37.311 --> 25:38.945
I'll go back to Ivan

25:38.979 --> 25:41.014
and I'll tell him that I'm
not supporting Nick Miner,

25:41.048 --> 25:42.849
and I'm throwing your
hat in the ring instead.

25:42.883 --> 25:44.784
