25:58.899 --> 26:00.667
Hey!

26:00.701 --> 26:01.701
Glad you're here actually.

26:01.736 --> 26:04.471
Tell me, is this relatively even?

26:05.673 --> 26:06.706
Yeah, looks good.

26:08.609 --> 26:11.089
Shouldn't you be preparing for
your honor board thing tomorrow?

26:12.246 --> 26:13.607
What's to prepare? I didn't cheat.

26:13.614 --> 26:15.515
I'm gonna tell them that.

26:15.549 --> 26:18.385
Do you know how hard this
must have been to find?

26:18.419 --> 26:20.987
An actual handwritten letter of hers?

26:21.021 --> 26:23.256
I've looked online. They
don't even sell these anymore.

26:23.290 --> 26:25.859
Most of them are in museums.

26:25.893 --> 26:27.293
Are you sure it's real?

26:27.328 --> 26:29.996
Of course it's real. He said it was real.

26:30.965 --> 26:33.066
Are you sure everything he says is true?

26:33.100 --> 26:34.968
You taking lessons now from dad?

26:35.002 --> 26:36.002
How to dump on Angelo.

26:39.039 --> 26:40.640
I found out something.

26:40.674 --> 26:42.525
Whatever, Toby.

26:42.560 --> 26:43.643
I probably shouldn't say anything, but...

26:43.677 --> 26:45.678
I feel like I need to tell you.

26:47.782 --> 26:49.449
Okay, he's my family.

26:49.483 --> 26:51.184
And you don't have to like him,

26:51.218 --> 26:53.219
but I won't have you talking
crap about him either.

26:54.488 --> 26:57.123
Bay, he got some chick pregnant.

27:00.094 --> 27:02.996
African-American and gorgeous?

27:03.030 --> 27:04.898
You know?

27:05.966 --> 27:06.966
Yeah.

27:07.001 --> 27:09.769
