A lot of people were calling

27:16.143 --> 27:17.977
and asking for statements.

27:19.847 --> 27:21.881
Do you think Regina and Daphne know?

27:21.916 --> 27:24.484
I think you and I are
the only people who know.

27:26.654 --> 27:27.587
It sucks.

27:27.621 --> 27:29.255
I'm sorry.

27:37.251 --> 27:38.491
This is a great school.

27:40.888 --> 27:41.855
Buckner.

27:41.889 --> 27:43.323
You are so lucky to go here.

27:45.259 --> 27:46.926
Sure am.

27:49.764 --> 27:51.765
You know what that means, right?

27:53.033 --> 27:54.868
"In unity, happiness."

27:54.902 --> 27:57.604
Very true. I agree.

28:00.741 --> 28:03.510
So that "People" magazine article,

28:03.544 --> 28:05.445
I never saw that.

28:05.479 --> 28:07.380
Did it ever come out?

28:11.152 --> 28:12.385
You can come in now.

28:12.403 --> 28:15.188
Uh, I don't know. I will find out.

28:15.222 --> 28:16.322
Come on.

28:20.177 --> 28:22.061
We... we go for walks.

28:22.079 --> 28:23.863
We, uh, watch movies.

28:23.897 --> 28:25.799
All in pure français.

28:25.833 --> 28:28.201
You see, Bay doesn't only learn from books.

28:28.235 --> 28:30.903
She needs to do, not just study.

28:30.921 --> 28:34.057
We're the same like that.

28:34.108 --> 28:37.627
Actually, we're the same in a lot of ways.

28:40.915 --> 28:42.582
You have one more minute.

28:42.616 --> 28:44.684
Is there anything else you'd like to add?

28:44.718 --> 28:46.820
Yes, on a personal note,

28:46.854 --> 28:48.655
I know my daughter.

28:48.689 --> 28:51.591
She's not a liar or a cheater.

28:51.625 --> 28:54.427
If she says something is true...

28:54.462 --> 28:56.429
it's true.

28:57.465 --> 28:58.431
Thank you.

29:01.402 --> 29:02.552
I think it went well.

29:02.603 --> 29:04.137
Mm-hmm.

29:04.171 --> 29:05.171
You're welcome.

29:05.189 --> 29:06.372
Thank you.

29:06.407 --> 29:08.408
Bay, what's going on?

29:12.213 --> 29:14.481
You told me she was a reporter.

29:14.515 --> 29:17.083
You looked me in the eye and you... 

29:17.117 --> 29:18.418
