29:18.452 --> 29:21.120
Is that who you are? A liar and
a cheater? How could you do that...

29:21.155 --> 29:23.990
Hold on a second! Regina and
I were not married back then.

29:24.024 --> 29:26.059
But you were with her.

29:26.093 --> 29:27.727
And how could you be so careless?

29:27.761 --> 29:29.028
They hammer into our
heads to use protection,

29:29.063 --> 29:31.798
