on a one night stand?!

29:31.832 --> 29:33.616
I am not talking about this with you, okay?

29:33.667 --> 29:34.734
You really don't have a choice.

29:34.752 --> 29:36.603
Because she exists now,

29:36.637 --> 29:37.737
and we all have to deal with it.

29:37.771 --> 29:39.839
No. This is my problem.

29:39.874 --> 29:41.474
And I'm taking care of it.

29:41.509 --> 29:42.709
What does that mean?

29:42.743 --> 29:44.711
I will give her whatever she wants

29:44.745 --> 29:46.479
to help raise...

29:46.514 --> 29:47.514
The baby.

29:49.149 --> 29:51.417
I don't think she wants
anything to do with me.

29:51.452 --> 29:55.288
So don't worry. Nothing
will change with us.

29:55.322 --> 29:57.323
Nothing will change?

29:57.358 --> 30:00.293
No. That's right.

30:00.361 --> 30:03.796
This is such déjà vu, you have no idea.

30:03.831 --> 30:05.911
Bay, don't walk away from
me when I'm talking to you.

30:05.916 --> 30:07.733
You're just gonna walk out on another kid.

30:07.751 --> 30:09.903
This is not the same!

30:09.937 --> 30:12.071
It is to the kid!

30:12.106 --> 30:13.940
You're gonna leave her or him

